President Muhammadu Buhari is set to visit Lekki Free Trade Zone, Lagos on Tuesday. According to Eons Intelligence in a Twitter post on Sunday, the President is visiting to commission Dangote Fertilizer Plant and inspect Lekki Deep Sea Port. Envisage. The tweet read, “JUST IN: President Muhammadu Buhari will visit Lekki Free Trade Zone, Lagos on Tuesday to commission Dangote Fertilizer Plant & inspect Lekki Deep Sea Port. “Envisage heightened security presence & potential traffic within the Lekki axis. Plan your itinerary. Plan your Journey!”